Wikisource Vietnamese — license summary
=======================================

Files: *.txt
- Underlying works (Chu Mạnh Trinh, Đoàn Quì, et al.): public domain
  (authors deceased >70 years; Vietnamese law and most jurisdictions).
- Wikisource transcriptions and editorial work: CC-BY-SA 4.0.
- Effective wrapper license: CC-BY-SA 4.0.

Attribution: "Vietnamese Wikisource contributors" + link to each title's
canonical page on https://vi.wikisource.org.

Full license text: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/

Use, modify, redistribute freely. Share-alike applies.
